OL,3,CParents left frustrated after
OL,4,Cneurodiverse diagnosis waiting times
OL,5,Cdouble
OL,7,FVictoria Rathbone is becoming
OL,8,Fincreasingly frustrated and upset as
OL,9,Fshe waits for her young son William,
OL,10,Fwho is four, to be put on the pathway
OL,11,Fthat will get him the help she says he
OL,12,Fneeds.
OL,14,FShe says she was told in 2022 he was
OL,15,Fnear the top of the waiting list but
OL,16,Ffour months into 2024 she is still
OL,17,Fwaiting and it has left her worried
OL,18,Fand confused.
OL,20,FHer youngest daughter Eva is also on
OL,21,Fthe pathway.
