OL,7,FShe said: "Life can be difficult on a
OL,8,Fdaily basis. It's quite stressful. And
OL,9,Fwe found this time around with my
OL,10,Fyoungest two that things are very
OL,11,Fdifferent to what they were when my
OL,12,Foldest was diagnosed.J"Obviously we
OL,13,Fhave a shortage of medical
OL,14,Fprofessionals, I think at the moment
OL,15,Fin the . So we haven't really been
OL,16,Freceiving any intervention as such and
OL,17,Fso it's difficult for support."
