OL,7,FVictoria added: "I think we need a new
OL,8,Fsystem. The current system is broken.
OL,9,FI think we need early intervention. I
OL,10,Fthink we need intervention whilst on
OL,11,Fthe waiting list for an assessment. I
OL,12,Fthink we need more professionals
OL,13,Finvolved in that intervention and I
OL,14,Fthink we ideally should be looking at
OL,15,Fa diagnosis within the very most 18
OL,16,Fmonths and I think particularly
OL,17,Fsupport for the parents who are going
OL,18,Fthrough this, particularly first time
OL,19,Fparents."
