OL,3,CParents left frustrated after
OL,4,Cneurodiverse diagnosis waiting times
OL,5,Cdouble
OL,7,FHe said: "We in the health board here
OL,8,Fin North Wales are experiencing a
OL,9,Fmassive increase in demand, the same
OL,10,Fas many other health care
OL,11,Forganisations across the UK and indeed
OL,12,Facross Europe. Three or four years ago
OL,13,Fwe would see perhaps 200 new referrals
OL,14,Fevery month. Now we're seeing 400, a
OL,15,Fdoubling of the demand in the space of
OL,16,Fonly a few years.J"That puts intense
OL,17,Fpressure on those waiting. Those
OL,18,Findividuals, their families and their
OL,19,Fcarers, but also on our staff who
OL,20,Freally want to do the right thing and
OL,21,Frespond to that demand. It's
OL,22,Fincredibly challenging."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/12
