OL,7,FDr Lyons continued: "That's perhaps
OL,8,Fwhere we really need to continue to
OL,9,Fdirect our efforts, ensuring that we
OL,10,Fcommunicate well with those people who
OL,11,Fare on our waiting lists and those
OL,12,Fpeople who are being seen."
OL,14,FHowever, Dr Lyons does not feel the
OL,15,Fissue comes down to a lack of funding.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/12
